{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A dynamic first-person action shooter in which you play the role of an experienced ghost hunter fighting the growing threat of otherworldly creatures. The goal of the game is to clear the location of ghosts using a variety of weapons, skills and upgrades. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ghosts will constantly attack you. Move and shoot at them. At your disposal will be: cartridges, rockets and grenades. As you progress through the game, you will earn money and experience, allowing you to upgrade your character's skills. These are skills that increase the speed of movement and damage of shells. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game will offer you to meet with different types of ghosts. As you progress through the game, new ghosts will appear, faster and stronger. To defeat them, you will need to improve your skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">By purchasing the game you will receive: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- 60 levels in an exciting shooter game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- An exciting gaming experience in the action genre. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Dynamic and intense gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- A variety of locations and opponents. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- A system for upgrading skills and upgrading weapons.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355120/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733301210","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355120/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733301210","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355120/6c8f185ba6163a611553f006d3feaa0e4a1dff97/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733301210","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355120/6c8f185ba6163a611553f006d3feaa0e4a1dff97/cap